content.p: If you would like to know more about research at the University of Nottingham, or have a particular enquiry, please contact us using the form below. The information that you provide in this form submission will be held in accordance with the Data Protection Act 2018 and the General Data Protection Regulation. Your personal data will be collected and processed by the University of Nottingham for the purpose of responding to your enquiry. The University of Nottingham will only use your personal information as set out in our privacy policy. University Park Nottingham NG7 2RD +44 (0) 115 951 5151 research@nottingham.ac.uk
